{
  "stem": "26576.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I also-- I wanted to be like everybody else.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But later on I realized that that would have been very stupid, if I would do it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I didn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I never did it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And also because I was a very bright student, they wanted me to join.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know, they wanted me to participate in everything.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it was a bit of a handicap.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But I never joined.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Especially a bit later on, later on, like, we had a teacher that came back.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "In Russia it was a big thing if you came back from the front, let's say, many people were-- lost their legs, hands, whatever.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I remember a teacher.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Every girl was in love with him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He came back from the front.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He had something which was called contusio, like he was paralyzed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "One hand was paralyzed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And he was a Cossack, and everybody which really he was not Cossack, he was a Tatar.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And everybody was-- the girls were in love with him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We were already 16.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And he said something, he said a joke about Stalin, and a few days later he disappeared.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "You know, this was the time when they were disappearing, and one was scared to open their mouth.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we heard all the stories that this was [NON-ENGLISH], and that one that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So-- so, we really were scared.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And my parents kept away from everything that could be-- their religion.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But everybody knew.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "All the-- all their other friends were Jewish.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And although I had not Jewish friends also, but the bulk of it were a Jewish kids, Russian Jewish kids in the school even.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I remember also there was a lot going on, in-- in-- in that Merke.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
